
#primary.content-area
  / Featured Content / Start
  #featured-content.clearfix.no-padding
    .container
      .col-sm-4
        .viewcode-example
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-body
              %p
                = image_tag "PSHQ-Entrepreneur-300-250.jpg"
            .panel-footer
              %a.btn.btn-danger.block{:href => '/podcasts', :style => 'display: block; width: 100%;color: white;'} Check out the Podcasts

      .col-sm-8
        .viewcode-example
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-heading
              %a.btn.btn-pshq-blue.block{:href => '/', :style => 'display: block; width: 100%;color: white;'} Are you the 2015 Entrepreneur?   
            .panel-body{:style => 'height: 250px;'}
              .tools
                %ul.nav.nav-tabs{:role => "tablist"}
                  %li{'ng-class' => "tabControl.checkIfActive('general')"}
                    %a{"data-toggle" => "tab", :href => "", 'ng-click' => "tabControl.changeView('general')", :style => 'color: black;'} General Details
                  %li{'ng-class' => "tabControl.checkIfActive('winners')"}
                    %a{"data-toggle" => "tab", :href => "", 'ng-click' => "tabControl.changeView('winners')", :style => 'color: black;'} Winners

              %br
              .tab-content
                #tab_1{'ng-if' => "tabControl.currentView === 'general'"}
                  %p.make-black
                    Problem Solution HQ, (PSHQ) is looking for partners that support our mission statement to “Help people every day with useful products that enrich their businesses and lives.” 
                  %p.make-black
                    Qualified applicants will share their accomplishments and future visions on their own Podcast distributed to our network of business partners and thought leaders.
                  %p.make-black
                    Listeners will be asked to vote for the PSHQ Entrepreneur over a 90 day period.
                  %p.make-black
                    Votes will be collected through various social media sites to strongly influence the decision of the partners of PSHQ when selecting their next Entrepreneur Partner!

                #tab_2{'ng-if' => "tabControl.currentView === 'winners'"}
                  .col-sm-6
                    %p.make-black
                      The Entrepreneur will receive:
                    %p.make-black
                      Professional consultations with the partners of PSHQ including
                    %p.make-black
                      Product evaluation and competitive market analysis
                    %p.make-black
                      Assistance in developing a business plan and pro-forma
                    / %p.make-black
                    /   Evaluation of required barriers to entry for the competition
                    / %p.make-black
                    /   Introductions to the PSHQ network of business partners
                  .col-sm-6
                    %p.make-black 
                      Percent equity in products developed through our combined efforts
                    %p.make-black
                      Support in soliciting venture-capital
                    %p.make-black
                      Resources and experience to build and market their product
                    %p.make-black
                      All applicants will retain their podcast for their own marketing efforts

            .panel-footer
              %a.btn.btn-pshq-green.block{:href => '/', :style => 'display: block; width: 100%;color: white;'} If you qualify to be The Next PSHQ Entrepreneur Register now!


